{"tid":2387610,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"GME logic 研究 (未讀過書)","createTime":"2021-01-30T12:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T13:01:02.000Z","uid":197112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b02757f90480e25bbfa3cfa1dd994085b59b5892","tid":2387610,"uid":197112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T12:26:47.000Z","msg":"見到有人話啲野可以借完再借， 所以可以 over 140%.<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就唔係好明呢個 logic <br />\n<br />\n假設市場有2個蘋果，a 有一個會借或賣， b 有一個但唔會借出。<br />\n<br />\na 借比 c 為期5日時間 , <br />\nc 賣比 d,<br />\nd 借比 e <br />\ne 食左個蘋果或者帶落官棺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5日之後， 租借期完結， a 要求c 還番個蘋果比佢。<br />\n<br />\n由於市場上面 第一個蘋果比人食左，c 只能向b 買， <br />\n所以b 開任何價錢，  例如5萬， c 都要接受，否則 a 會日日向c 收雙倍蘋果價值嘅息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買左 GME 唔放嘅人 係咪阿 b？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雷曼個時係咪咁爆？ 成班阿c 還唔到貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />純邏輯討論， 有冇金融才俊解答一下岩唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb190d3543cee41140256191dde2d161bea3b48","tid":2387610,"uid":53127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"A借股票比B沽空, B賣比C<br />\n<br />\nD又借比E沽空，E賣比F<br />\n<br />\n宜家要要平倉，F sh唔賣，C賣左比E<br />\n<br />\nE拎左黎平倉，去返D, D借比B平倉還返比A<br />\n<br />\n如果仲係平唔晒倉，A又借返比E平倉<br />\n<br />\n咁咪變左永動機，F sh變左傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7fad12de666befb5cbad2a27d1cb2890545d3d","tid":2387610,"uid":154594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efb190d3543cee41140256191dde2d161bea3b48","tid":2387610,"uid":53127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"A借股票比B沽空, B賣比C